1.*Dobar* dan! (Good day!)
2. On je *dobra* osoba. (He is a good person.) 
3. *Dobro* je da je došao. (It's good that he came.) 
4. Ona je veoma *dobra* učenica. (She is a very good student.) 
5. *Dobro* je da smo se videli. (It's good that we saw each other.) 
6. On je veoma *dobar* prijatelj. (He is a very good friend.)